# Student Management System using SQL

This project demonstrates the implementation of a Student Management System using MySQL. 
It showcases fundamental and intermediate SQL concepts by creating a relational database consisting of Students, Courses, and Enrollments tables.



## Technologies Used

- MySQL
- SQL

##  Database Structure

The database consists of three tables:

### Students
- Student ID
- Name
- Email
- City
- Enrollment Date

### Courses
- Course ID
- Course Name
- Course Fee

### Enrollments
- Enrollment ID
- Student ID (Foreign Key)
- Course ID (Foreign Key)

